heading: 2. The 31st day of August 2024 is appointed as the day on which the
text_raw:
2. The 31st day of August 2024 is appointed as the day on which the 
Criminal Law (Sexual Offences and Human Trafficking) Act 2024 (No. 28 of 
2024), other than Part 3, shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

31 July, 2024. 

HELEN MCENTEE, 
Minister for Justice. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 2nd August, 2024.
